IN THE CIRCUIT COURT OF THE FIFTEENTH JUDICIAL CIRCUIT IN AND FOR PALM BEACH COUNTY, FLORIDA CRIMINAL DIVISION "W"
INV GREGORY A. PARKINSON #8717 PALM BEACH POLICE DEPARTMENT 345 S. COUNTY ROAD PALM BEACH, FL 33480
CASE NO:2006CF009454AMB AGENCY CASE NO. 76-05-0368 CRIME LAB NO.
STATE OF FLORIDA
V.
JEFFREY E EPSTEIN
ONE WEEK DOCKET - REMAIN ON CALL
March 12, 2008
This case has been set for trial beginning the week of 07/08/2008 at 9:30 a.m., Palm Beach County Courthouse, 205 North Dixie Highway, COURTROOM 11F, West Palm Beach, Florida.
Please call the State Attorney's Office at (561) 355-7376 the working day prior to the above date, after 2:00 p.m. to verify time of trial. You may also contact this office via email at COMBALI2@SA15.STATE.FL.US. This subpoena is binding day to day and week to week until the case is closed.
Sincerely,
LANNA BELLOHAVEK Assistant State Attorney
If you are a person with a disability who needs any accommodation in order to participate in this proceeding, you are entitled, at no cost to you, to the provision of certain assistance. Please contact the ADA Coordinator in the Administrative Office of the Court, Palm Beach County Courthouse, 205 North Dixie Highway, Room 5.2500, West Palm Beach, Florida, 33401; telephone number (561) 355-4380 within two (2) working days of your receipt of this notice; if you are hearing or voice impaired, call 1-800-955-8771.
DATE ISSUED March 12, 2008
